{"tid":1970790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林榮基來台一年 銅鑼灣書店25日台北開幕","createTime":"2020-04-13T11:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T07:24:16.000Z","uid":254183,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c9107bfe99509a8ed56817244abd5a182e5655","tid":1970790,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/04/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%A2-%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97-20200412124033_b6a7_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258C%2597-20200412124033_b6a7_large.jpg&h=6efed75a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/04/%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97-%E6%9E%97%E6%A6%AE%E5%9F%BA-20200412133217_1be0_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258C%2597-%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%259F%25BA-20200412133217_1be0_large.jpg&h=581d340b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/04/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%A2-%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97-20200412124059_51e0_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258C%2597-20200412124059_51e0_large.jpg&h=ef05e6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/04/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B3%A2-%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97-20200412133103_2602_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258C%2597-20200412133103_2602_large.jpg&h=59f160a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/04/%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97-%E9%93%9C%E9%94%A3%E6%B9%BE%E4%B9%A6%E5%BA%97-20200412124130_4353_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F04%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258C%2597-%25E9%2593%259C%25E9%2594%25A3%25E6%25B9%25BE%25E4%25B9%25A6%25E5%25BA%2597-20200412124130_4353_large.jpg&h=fb425498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者張淑伶台北11日電）資金由群募支持的銅鑼灣書店25日將在台北開幕。前香港銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基說，疫情緣故不會特別辦活動，避免人潮聚集，但歡迎台灣人未來多到店裡看看。<br />\n<br />\n林榮基在電話中告訴中央社記者，選4月25日開幕其實並沒有特殊的理由，但這是給所有參與群眾募資者的承諾。由於武漢肺炎的疫情，要避免人群聚集，加上林榮基本人不愛湊熱鬧，所以當天不會辦特別的活動。<br />\n<br />\n他說，「公共衛生還是比較重要」，想來逛書店，不一定要選在開幕日，他歡迎台灣人多來看看。<br />\n<br />\n林榮基說，書店中的特色之一是台灣研究類書籍，因為台灣人不只要在面對中國時認識自己，平常就應當更了解自己的歷史和文化；書店內也會有包括童書在內的各類書籍。<br />\n<br />\n他並表示會好好挑書，一些內容比較表面、觀點較為單一的評論著作，他會避免挑選。<br />\n<br />\n書店店址選在南京西路5-1號10樓、捷運中山站3號出口附近，目前各項籌備工作都差不多了，林榮基在台的工作簽證也在申請中。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓銅鑼灣書店在台灣重啟，去年9月到11月間網上募得近新台幣600萬元，據了解，目前在裝修等各方面已用了約150萬元。<br />\n<br />\n當時募資活動的口號是「為自由的靈魂而開」，林榮基說，希望開一家不只是買賣書的書店，而是作家、經營者與讀者交流思想的平台。<br />\n<br />\n去年的4月25日，其實是林榮基決定遠走家鄉，來台「避難」的日子。<br />\n<br />\n林榮基2015年遭中國大陸警方拘捕，後來他趁返港之時公開被拘留的細節，並表示不會再到中國大陸。2019年4月25日，他從香港搭機來台，指香港官方堅持修訂「逃犯條例」，他已經沒有再留下的理由。<br />\n<br />\n時隔一年，香港人歷經風起雲湧的「反送中」抗爭；香港「銅鑼灣書店事件」中，前股東桂民海也在中國因「為境外非法提供情報」罪名被判監禁10年；銅鑼灣書店則在林榮基的努力下，今年4月25日將在台灣獲得新生。（編輯：張淑伶）1090411"},{"pid":"18c34d35890cea8c5f230c4b02aab25a69e850dd","tid":1970790,"uid":254183,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqNOoCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqNOoCs.jpg&h=59bf96a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNwvBXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNwvBXt.jpg&h=273193d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33pUjaO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33pUjaO.jpg&h=687975db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fu5wmo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFu5wmo9.jpg&h=2dcc488f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzWfN4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzWfN4a.jpg&h=f7a09540&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d8ac505dd9fb5a428415e094a5747f00a9b2c54","tid":1970790,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85964870bd1d9a7dc2dae74bbc8c4057932a97d3","tid":1970790,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"必訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704f840f183f5ad7886601df2c12f603b37d97e8","tid":1970790,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46e7bbb8f6f42042358bc815d0182e0f4fb16bb","tid":1970790,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a79d52539fc7f1722751db3695c57ab661f713a","tid":1970790,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"<i